com.decoded.zool

Class ZoolDataSinkImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.decoded.zool.ZoolDataSinkImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ZoolDataSink

    public class ZoolDataSinkImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ZoolDataSink
    The ZoolDataSink accepts data from a Zookeeper path watch. You can create any number of DataSink for a single node. Also, you may drain data from different nodes on the same Zool instance.
